thread.title: Julie

author: Julie
title: Julie
text: My experience with Joe and Truc has been second to none. From the realistic estimate of the market status, advice on the best selling strategy and continued feedback regarding the potential buyer activity. We have no reservations recommending both Joe and Truc for any property transactions. Of particular note is the fact that the team were extremely honest and responsive to any queries or questions through out the process. The auction day was a difficult, hot day and yet the team were able to exceed our expectations in the running of the auction and the successful outcome. Thank you for the professionalism and personal nature you put to this process to enable us to sell our first home.
